The paper proposes a novel end-to-end neural network model for time series classification, which incorporates feature extraction and classification in a single framework. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
